<h1>Dynamically process modeling and prototyping</h1>
</center>

<ul>
<li>Incrementally model and "enact" prototypes of process redesign alternatives
<li>Provide role-specific views of process task structure
<li>
Demonstration of as-is version of Grant Award process (shown at USC)
<li>Develop prototype transition strategy and reimplementation (next).
</ul>

