<center>
<h1>Wide-area process enactment environment</h1>
</center>

<ul>
<li>New process markup language (PML) for modeling process architectures
<li>PML compiler (generates process decomposition diagrams
and WWW-based  process enactment automatically)
<li>Internet-based execution system
<li>WWW-browser as Graphic User Interface (GUI) 
	to process enactment environment
<li>Distributed hypertext-based object management system
<li>Integration mechanisms for incorporating new/legacy IT systems (INRIS, etc.)
</ul>

<pre>

</pre>
